      "content": "That's a good start. Can you expand on the idea of the \"gatekeeper\" role? I want to argue that even \"soft\" regulations—like those meant to prevent misinformation or protect minors—are actually just slow-motion censorship. Is there a philosophical way to frame these common justifications as fundamentally illegitimate?",
